2. **Generate ≠ send.** If the user only says 生成 / 写 / 广告推广 / 营销模版 with **no recipient**, run `email-creative-builder`, show the draft, and **stop**. Do not call Resend/MCP send.
3. Send **only** when the user explicitly names a real recipient (发送给 / 发给 `user@domain`). Never invent `recipient@example.com` or other placeholders.
